#: Settings.ui:2600
msgid ""
"Temporarily show the application numbers over the icons, corresponding to "
"the shortcut."
msgstr ""
"Erakutsi une batez laster-teklei dagozkien aplikazio-zenbakiak ikonoen "
"gainean."

